body_html:
Thank you Vijay. I've been dealing with the same error after upgrade. Per recommendations above, tried
pip uninstall tensorflow
pip uninstall protobuf
pip install url/to/the/tensorflow-...whl
but the problem persisted.

Then tried
pip uninstall tensorflow
pip uninstall protobuf
manually deleted tensorboard.py from /usr/local/bin
pip install url/to/the/tensorflow-...whl
tensorboard.py was recreated with the new tensorflow installation and the problem resolved.
